Correctly apply GENIOSIL N45 in serpentine
lines to the back and then firmly press the

00:06:24.330 --> 00:06:29.500
mirror to the wall in the desired position.

00:06:29.500 --> 00:06:36.500
For large mirrors, apply the beads in vertical,
parallel lines.

